=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114560/extras/1486ad67cf5c5e33a49f24f79e6c766d.poster.avif?t=1662656440\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114560/extras/1486ad67cf5c5e33a49f24f79e6c766d.webm?t=1662656440\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make a Selfie</h2><br>Onoskelis may not smile as cute as Succubus, but especially for you,<br>she will start snapping her jaws as soon as you ask her, presenting herself in two new positions, characteristic of its species.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feature list:</h2><br>- Onoskelis Skin<br>- Onoskelis Skin (ice)<br>- 4 new special powers<br>- Onoskelis voiceovers<br>- 2 new selfie poses",
